node.text: Sometimes the only time we hearing loving supporting language is when that special someone comes around to remind us that there is goodness and hope to be found if only we can look for it. It’s my opinion that one of the most crucial self realizations is we must learn to speak life, love, support, and energy into ourselves! Plug into the endless supply of ALL that is and access whatever it is you need today! Anytime, it’s ours to access. Hands on our heart ♥️ and hear this message with an open heart. Xo

node.text: Grow? If so, firstly I’d like to point out that is incredibly normal and understandable. It’s hard to walk off the beaten path laid out by your “tribe” to pursue your own ambitions. Bravo to you for taking the narrow path. Your life is the best example you can live. So as you expand, you are expanding possibility for your loved ones! May not always feel like winning, but a life lived authentically, beyond comfort and the expectations of others is a beacon of Light 💡. You are a way maker. The person with the shovel, clearing the path- That’s you. Visualize that, and that’s some back breaking work! By no means must you, but if you choose… you’ll be able to look at your life and say with confidence “I did all I could” and mean it.

Well, that’s what I did and the feedback was an incredible tool to dig deeper in this season, get more real, and gave me a cheat code to some confidence & areas I can still use work on! Getting through weeds* can be tough, use all the tools! The feedback is a tool 🔨

I’m really out in the backyard this summer because I swear it’s hotter than ever! Im really not trying to make anyone more comfortable by meeting expectations I have no business worrying about! I’m REALLY committed to seeing what this version of myself thats lookin for the adventure in the day to day is going to discover! That’s really what’s going on! I’m want to champion good things, that do good work, that make life better and remind the good people to be fully present and show up for life like it’s the big day! Starts with me~ Thanks for carrying on yall!

node.text: One of the things I always do is look for ways to make my lifestyle fun, disciplined, and spontaneous! It helps me to stay in appreciation for the process. I think it has given me years of longevity. So here I decided to have the “Get Results Bundle” close by so I could take everything starting with the Burn, then made some ice cold Body Juice to refresh and cool me down and had a nice workout poolside and the ab gel and waist trimmer went on to really finish it off. I lasted about 25 min before I had to get in that pool lol!

node.text: A core, a place from where it grows, flows and shines. These are questions I believe we all search to find an answer for. As I journey and live I find closer to the heart of true happiness. Not a constant state but also not so easily lost. When you know where to find truth you can access it much quicker when times get difficult. Something we should all consider ♥️

node.text: Anyone who knows me knows, we might be poolside in bikinis, huddled around the table for hours, standing in the kitchen with the same piece of food on the plate for too long because no matter where or when.. what we are gonna do IS TALK ABOUT LIFE, share perspective, laugh, im 💯 going to say something about something random that is going to make you laugh, and if the sun comes out... Kathy is gonna stand in it- And I’m going to bring you with me! Maybe today you need to find the patch of sunshine that pops through the clouds and hurry to go stand it it. Could change everything! Thank God for seasons that continue to change. Look for your sunshine today ⛅️

node.title: Here’s what we ARE GONNA DO!

node.text: Roll with me for 60 seconds to get encouraged- Have you experienced it? Those amazing moments whether on vacation, while working on a project or getting QT with a loved one- When you feel ALL THE WAY HERE! Let me put it this way... being Fully present is taking a vacation from distraction! I believe if we can achieve less distracted, more present living- A Better quality of life is instantly achievable🤟🏽

node.title: The POWER of being present is undeniable.

node.text:
•
I’ve settled on a word rather than a sentence because I know things are about to get busy so easy and simple to remember the word is PRESENCE! The best of me shows up (no matter the weather ☀️ 🌧) when I am present in this life journey. How often are we here but really “there”? Somewhere in the past or in the worries/ anticipation/ fear/ of the future. When all the while, our moments are happening and need us here! So I cruised nice and slow and quietly to the beach today and played in the waves, laid out on the sand and reminded myself that slowing down is ALWAYS a good idea because I naturally move fast! Not bad for business, but you can miss a lot when your always on GO. Have the best rest tonight and my prayer is that we would show up fully present tomorrow🙏🏽 gnight fam.

It was NOT intentional that I had this whole Bey* situation on and was inspired by an incredible story of forgiveness** and renewing** that forgiveness brings! But it happened, and I ain’t mad! What happens when you release forgiveness? When you lay down the baggage 🧳 that is offense, pain, rage, distrust... don’t get it twisted- it’s a self service! Forgiveness is the greatest FREE gift we can receive without ever having to see the offender face-2-face! Listen and you’ll see. There may be a few lemons needing to be made into lemonade in our hearts. That’s alright, there’s grace and endless love for that. The forgiver is a Free person! Free, no strings attached!

node.title: LEMONADE 🍋 LEMONS 🍋 Medicine for the Soul.

node.text: A sister who also calls herself a coach started commenting all over my page that I wasn’t fit. I blocked her immediately. Darn, I should have posted this video first. Hopefully one day we learn that we all we got. There  is so much beauty in bigging up our brother or sister. Especially if you are black or brown. We will get there one day. Anywho, back to my weekly progression checkup. Building while slowly toning.

node.text: I’ve always been a smoothie queen 👑 I love them, in all the endless variety they offer! This one I simply used dragon fruit, almond milk and Vanilla ThickQuick to get this bright pink flavorful meal. It fits perfectly into my plan…Protein, healthy fats, and just the right amount of whole food carbs to give me the fuel for my workouts & plenty of energy.

node.text: Sometimes the only time we hearing loving supporting language is when that special someone comes around to remind us that there is goodness and hope to be found if only we can look for it. It’s my opinion that one of the most crucial self realizations is we must learn to speak life, love, support, and energy into ourselves! Plug into the endless supply of ALL that is and access whatever it is you need today! Anytime, it’s ours to access. Hands on our heart ♥️ and hear this message with an open heart. Xo

node.text: Waking up feels different when you’ve got a clear goal in mind. Living in dull lack of commitment energy will drain you 💯x more than working hard towards something you believe in. Belief in yourself, is no different than a muscle. If you don’t put it to work it won’t develop. Start, that’s the necessary 1st step.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kathy Freeman 🇹🇹 on July 29, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
I NEED…
The voice inside my damn head loves to start a sentence with “I need…” I will be strolling along on my evening walk and suddenly out of absolutely no where “I need…” sitting on the potty… scrolling and suddenly here she goes…”I need…” Tired after a hard workout and I hear her never ending request…”I need…” Busy full work day got me stressing, here she goes …”I need”. 

GIRL. Why you NEED so dang much though!?

What do you HAVE. 

Here is my self awareness challenge that I am sharing with you. Catch the “I need…” and stop it. Before it has the chance to subconsciously walk you to yet another mindless purchase, another caffeinated fix, another income wasting activity, another lazy choice…Instead, express your HAVE. Powerful. Try it for yourself  and see hit how much CONTROL you have been forfeiting to your “needs” instead of utilizing the resources both internally and externally that you already HAVE access to to create what is and can be and should be. Mindset shifting and Life shifting.

This is how I was raised to do it… Anyone else? And it is always served with a piece of toast to dip (soak!!) in the cup 😌 Very nice treat for the mid day rain/ and pick me up while working!

(Is the blowing in the can a Caribbean thing?? Please let me know!)
